{"page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     NorthgateArinso UK Limited\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Business Design and Business Process Design\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    The Business Design helps an organisation planning to move to a cloud-based solution to develop a clear understanding of how HR and payroll technology will be implemented, to plan its introduction.  One key output is a series of process \u2018swimlanes\u2019 to provide input for new HR and payroll delivery structures.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Includes both system and non-system process steps and documentation requirements\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Clear accountability &amp; responsibilities for each process\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Confirmation that requirements can be met through standard system functionality\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Defined business benefits of deploying the newly design processes\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Management information requirements linked to each process in scope\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Identified change management considerations\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Improved alignment of strategy, process and technology\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Project risk is reduced\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Potential problems are identified early\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Deeper understanding of HR system use and implications\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     The Business Design supports decisions such as project phasing\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     The focus is on change management\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Provides the basis for job and organisational design\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3700.0 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Termination costs apply\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/579492/4934398789025792-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/579492/4934398789025792-sfia-rate-card.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/579492/4934398789025792-service-definition-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Service definition\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/579492/4934398789025792-terms-and-conditions.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Terms and conditions\n      </a>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Framework\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"external-link-default\">\n     <a href=\"http://ccs-agreements.cabinetoffice.gov.uk/contracts/rm1557vi\" rel=\"external\">\n      G-Cloud 6\n     </a>\n    </div>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Service ID\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"service-id\">\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      4934\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      3987\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      8902\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      5792\n     </span>\n    </div>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Contact\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"contact-details\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Organization\">\n     <p class=\"contact-details-organisation\">\n      <span itemprop=\"name\">\n       NorthgateArinso UK Limited\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p class=\"contact-details-block\">\n      <span itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\">\n       <span itemprop=\"name\">\n        Becky Cole\n       </span>\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p class=\"contact-details-block\">\n      <span itemprop=\"telephone\">\n       01733 397715\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p class=\"contact-details-block\">\n      <span itemprop=\"email\">\n       <a data-event-category=\"Email a supplier\" data-event-label=\"NorthgateArinso UK Limited\" href=\"mailto:bidsupport@ngahr.com\">\n        bidsupport@ngahr.com\n       </a>\n      </span>\n     </p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row service-attributes\">\n  <div class=\"column-one-whole\">\n   <h2 class=\"summary-item-heading\">\n    Support\n   </h2>\n   <table class=\"summary-item-body\">\n    <caption class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Support\n    </caption>\n    <thead class=\"summary-item-field-headings\">\n     <tr>\n